stimated for various crude supper feed rates and coal feed rates. However there is a slight distinction in the acquired temperature, the general temperature evaluation process doesn't show a huge contrast as per the dataset. © 2022, The Author(s), under exclusive licence to Springer Science+Business Media, LLC, part of Springer Nature.},
